name: RotaJetONE
description:
Use forces on a rotating jet-sphere to navigate tricky courses and get to the orange exit!

BETA Build, more levels will be added in the future

CONTROLS

Fire Jet: Spacebar

Restart: r

Everything Else: Mouse click

Your Time score's are saved to your browsers cache. Clearing your browsers cache will delete your save data. You can also clear your data in game, on the bottom right on the home and level selector pages
